# Design Tokens

## Colors (Tailwind)
```js
colors: {
  teal: { DEFAULT: '#1A8A7D', dark: '#14706A', light: '#E6F5F3' },
  text: { primary: '#1E293B', secondary: '#64748B', muted: '#94A3B8' },
  surface: { DEFAULT: '#FAFAF8', card: '#FFFFFF', border: '#E8E5E0', divider: '#F1EDE8' },
  accent: { orange: '#E8913A', red: '#DC4F4F', green: '#3BA676' },
  ai: { bubble: '#F5F0EB' },
}
```

## Typography
- Headings: `font-serif` (Source Serif 4)
- Body: `font-sans` (DM Sans)
- Page title: 28px serif 600
- Section: 22px serif 600
- Card title: 18px sans 600
- Body: 16px sans 400
- Caption: 14px sans 400
- Hero number: 48px serif 700
- **Minimum: 14px anywhere**

## Spacing
- Screen padding: px-5 (20px)
- Card padding: p-5 (20px)
- Tab bar: 72px tall (not default 56px)

## Components
- Primary button: h-14 (56px), rounded-btn (12px)
- Tap targets: min h-12 w-12, 8px between
- Cards: rounded-card (16px), shadow-card, border

## Motion
- 250ms ease-out
- Card entrance: fade + translateY(8px), stagger 50ms
- Respect prefers-reduced-motion
- Never: bounce, shake, spin
